@clientEmail = client01@email.com
@clientPassword = 12345678
@profId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### Login do CLIENT (define {{token}})
POST {{base_url}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{clientEmail}}",
  "password": "{{clientPassword}}"
}

> {% client.global.set("token", response.body.token); %}

### Lista avaliações do profissional (qualquer autenticado)
GET {{base_url}}/api/professionals/{{profId}}/reviews
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Avaliar profissional — 201 (CLIENT). Repetir atualiza a mesma avaliação.
POST {{base_url}}/api/professionals/{{profId}}/reviews
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Serviço excelente, recomendo!"
}

### Lista de novo — deve incluir a avaliação acima
GET {{base_url}}/api/professionals/{{profId}}/reviews
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Perfil do profissional — averageRating e reviewCount agora refletem as avaliações
GET {{base_url}}/api/professionals/{{profId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Nota inválida — 422 VALIDATION_ERROR
POST {{base_url}}/api/professionals/{{profId}}/reviews
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 9
}
